# ASCEND .trivyignore example
# Copy to your repo root as .trivyignore and customize.
# Format: one CVE ID per line. Optional expiration after "exp:YYYY-MM-DD".

# Example: unfixable CVE in base image — revisit after 2026-06-01 base image update
# CVE-2024-12345  exp:2026-06-01

# Example: false positive — vendored library not actually reachable
# CVE-2024-67890

# Example: accepted risk documented in SECURITY_EXCEPTIONS.md
# CVE-2024-99999
